<font color="#ffff00">අන්තිමේදි, නූඩ්ල්.</font>

1567
01:22:19,484 --> 01:22:21,959
<font color="#ffff00">ලොකුම ගොඩ.</font>

1568
01:22:21,959 --> 01:22:24,192
